def c1 := 30000000000 + 10000000000
def c2 := 40000000000
def c3 := fact 10
def v1  := 3628800
def v2  := 3628801
#guard_msgs in
#eval checkDefEq `c3 `v1
#guard_msgs in
#eval checkDefEq `c1 `c2
def c4 := decide (100000000 < 20000000000)
#guard_msgs in
#eval checkDefEq `c4 `Bool.true
def c5 := "h".length
def c6 := 1
set_option pp.all true
#guard_msgs in
#eval checkDefEq `c5 `c6
def c7 := decide ("hello" = "world")
#guard_msgs in
#eval whnf `c8
def c9  : String := "hello" ++ "world"
def c10 : String := "helloworld"
#guard_msgs in
#eval whnf `c11
def c12 : Nat := 'a'.toNat
#guard_msgs in
#eval check `c11
